article_title: Democrat Elisabeth Jensen to square off against U.S. Rep Andy Barr in the fall
article_text: Central Kentucky Democrats chose political newcomer Elisabeth Jensen on Tuesday as their nominee to challenge U.S. Rep. Andy Barr, R-Lexington, in the Nov. 4 election.
